The paper discusses secure computation and simulation in interactive systems, which is a topic closely related to cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also deals with asynchronous systems, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and information theory (cs.IT). The construction provided in the paper involves algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), and the additional security properties discussed in the paper may involve machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG).
